00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:24,000
That's right. It was probably on my grandfather's model, whoever the leader was in every neighborhood or who exactly, you know, people looked up to.

335
00:32:24,000 --> 00:32:26,000
Yeah. So you were the man or woman.

